exercises.name: Push-ups
exercises.description: Push-ups are a great bodyweight exercise that primarily targets the chest, shoulders, and triceps.

exercises.name: Squats
exercises.description: Squats are a fundamental lower body exercise that targets the quadriceps, hamstrings, and glutes.

exercises.name: Pull-ups
exercises.description: Pull-ups are a challenging upper body exercise that primarily targets the back, biceps, and shoulders.

exercises.name: Deadlifts
exercises.description: Deadlifts are a compound exercise that targets multiple muscle groups including the lower back, hamstrings, and glutes.

exercises.name: Bench Press
exercises.description: The bench press is a classic chest exercise that also works the shoulders and triceps.

exercises.name: Lunges
exercises.description: Lunges are a versatile lower body exercise that targets the quadriceps, hamstrings, and glutes.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Rows
exercises.description: Dumbbell rows are a great exercise for building a strong back and improving posture.

exercises.name: Leg Press
exercises.description: The leg press machine targets the quadriceps, hamstrings, and glutes with less stress on the lower back compared to squats.

exercises.name: Shoulder Press
exercises.description: Shoulder press targets the deltoid muscles of the shoulders and triceps.

exercises.name: Romanian Deadlifts
exercises.description: Romanian deadlifts focus on the hamstrings and glutes while also engaging the lower back.

exercises.name: Tricep Dips
exercises.description: Tricep dips are a bodyweight exercise that primarily targets the triceps.

exercises.name: Calf Raises
exercises.description: Calf raises target the calf muscles and are commonly done using bodyweight, dumbbells, or a calf raise machine.

exercises.name: Bicep Curls
exercises.description: Bicep curls isolate the biceps and are typically performed using dumbbells, barbells, or resistance bands.

exercises.name: Hamstring Curls
exercises.description: Hamstring curls target the hamstring muscles and can be performed using a machine or lying hamstring curl bench.

exercises.name: Planks
exercises.description: Planks are an excellent core exercise that also engage the shoulders, chest, and back.
